"""
        Test that the client can rekey an object.
        """
result = {'unique_identifier': '2', 'result_status': enums.ResultStatus.SUCCESS
    }
client = ProxyKmipClient()
client.open()
client.proxy.rekey.return_value = result
checked_id = client.rekey(uid='1', offset=0, activation_date=1000000,
    process_start_date=1000001, protect_stop_date=1000002,
    deactivation_date=1000003)
self.assertEqual('2', checked_id)
mock.patch('kmip.pie.client.KMIPProxy', mock.MagicMock(spec_set=KMIPProxy))
